WEBVTT

00:06.527 --> 00:09.368
These old Southern homes...

00:09.369 --> 00:12.909
There's so much more to
them than just a house.

00:12.910 --> 00:17.890
There was a tension, like
somebody was watching.

00:18.084 --> 00:22.164
I knew this house contained secrets.

00:22.408 --> 00:26.428
What Pandora did they just unleash?

00:27.759 --> 00:31.529
There was something in this house,
and it was trying to kill me.

00:31.530 --> 00:34.132
[Suspenseful music swelling]

00:34.133 --> 00:36.173
[Yelps]

00:38.788 --> 00:41.473
Y'all be careful in this house.

00:41.474 --> 00:42.941
[Screams]

00:42.942 --> 00:45.942
It's full of death.

00:49.418 --> 00:50.410
_.

00:50.411 --> 00:54.011
[Voice whispering indistinctly]

00:56.422 --> 01:00.022
[Reflective instrumental music]

01:02.600 --> 01:04.280
_.

01:06.229 --> 01:10.365
1991 had been a tough
year for our family.

01:10.366 --> 01:14.736
My stepfather was in insurance
sales, but work had dried up.

01:14.737 --> 01:18.070
And it dried up very quickly.

01:18.071 --> 01:23.374
I felt that I needed to look
beyond what I'd been doing.

01:23.375 --> 01:28.821
I decided to study to be a
preacher and to go to Seminary.

01:28.822 --> 01:34.722
I was very supportive of his decision,
but I knew it wouldn't be easy.

01:35.499 --> 01:40.654
We'd have to take a cut in
pay, and we needed to relocate.

01:40.655 --> 01:42.756
I didn't really want to move.

01:42.757 --> 01:45.309
I was gonna have to go to a new school.

01:45.310 --> 01:51.010
Being uprooted as a teenager
is a painful thing sometimes.

01:53.765 --> 01:57.425
We pulled into the driveway...

01:57.491 --> 02:03.011
And it was really gorgeous,
an old Southern farmhouse...

02:03.014 --> 02:04.772
From, like, the 1750s...

02:04.773 --> 02:05.802
Hi.

02:05.803 --> 02:10.842
With the wraparound porch
and the rocking chairs.

02:10.877 --> 02:14.952
It had been let go down by
the family that owned it.

02:14.953 --> 02:19.254
So it was in our budget
to rent; It was cheap.

02:19.255 --> 02:20.817
Welcome to paradise.

02:20.818 --> 02:23.185
The realtor met us
there when we pulled up.

02:23.186 --> 02:25.452
Come on. Come on, everybody.

02:25.453 --> 02:27.373
Yeah.

02:29.291 --> 02:34.751
To our surprise, the previous
tenants were still there.

02:35.481 --> 02:38.930
They were in the process of moving
out, but they weren't finished.

02:38.931 --> 02:40.564
Come, come, come. Come on.

02:40.565 --> 02:43.633
Come on, come on. Come right in.

02:43.634 --> 02:49.534
Couldn't get it out of my mind that there
was a reason for this house to be cheap.

02:53.959 --> 02:57.300
There was a padlocked door.

02:57.301 --> 03:03.201
Didn't make any sense to have a
padlocked door inside the house.

03:06.206 --> 03:10.839
The realtor was taking me around
the house and letting me know...

03:10.840 --> 03:14.545
What the rules were, so she said...

03:14.546 --> 03:18.247
Please, this rug here in this room, the
owners would like you to leave it there.

03:18.248 --> 03:19.715
It's really old and fragile.

03:19.716 --> 03:25.085
It was a rose-colored large rug
that filled the room pretty well.

03:25.086 --> 03:27.086
No problem.

03:27.087 --> 03:30.627
It's kind of a lovely rug.

03:31.957 --> 03:34.291
The lady was coming
out, and I asked her...

03:34.292 --> 03:37.060
Excuse me. What's behind this door?

03:37.061 --> 03:40.224
She had kind of a
shocked look on her face.

03:40.225 --> 03:43.297
She said, that was my Uncle's room.

03:43.298 --> 03:45.332
He committed suicide in there.

03:45.333 --> 03:46.800
Oh.

03:46.801 --> 03:51.721
Out of respect for him,
please keep it locked.

03:56.093 --> 03:58.733
This is creepy.

04:00.509 --> 04:02.076
A man died in this room.

04:02.077 --> 04:04.657
[Ominous music]

04:10.575 --> 04:12.975
[Door slams]

04:16.952 --> 04:20.685
Ah, we got to do
something about that roof.

04:20.687 --> 04:22.297
[Eerie voices whispering]

04:22.298 --> 04:23.855
Hey!

04:23.856 --> 04:27.291
She said, do not for any reason...

04:27.292 --> 04:29.467
Remove that rock from the door.

04:29.468 --> 04:31.947
Do not let the children play in there.

04:31.948 --> 04:35.252
I really didn't know
what the reason was,

04:35.253 --> 04:38.131
but I was like, okay,
this is a great place.

04:38.132 --> 04:40.485
It's got lots of land
for the kids to play on.

04:40.486 --> 04:43.334
Why would they need to be in there?

04:43.335 --> 04:45.856
Anyway, I... I just noticed the roof.

04:45.857 --> 04:51.757
To speed things up, I decided to give the
old tenants a hand, help them move out.

04:52.274 --> 04:56.714
- Thank you for your help.
- No worries.

04:56.977 --> 04:59.108
As she was walking away, she paused and

04:59.109 --> 05:01.848
turned back and looked
at me, and she said...

05:01.849 --> 05:05.689
Y'all be careful in this house.

05:06.720 --> 05:09.720
It's full of death.

05:11.257 --> 05:15.960
And she jumped in her
truck, and they were gone.

05:15.961 --> 05:18.128
[Echoing] Full of death...

05:18.129 --> 05:21.597
How do you react to something like
that? That's a bomb dropped on you.

05:21.598 --> 05:24.178
[Ominous music]

05:29.170 --> 05:31.405
I couldn't sleep that night.

05:31.406 --> 05:37.306
I was kind of wound up from what
she said when she was leaving.

05:39.395 --> 05:42.095
[Metal squeaking]

05:48.620 --> 05:52.520
I could see the doorknob turning.

05:52.790 --> 05:57.950
This was very late at
night. Everybody was asleep.

05:58.961 --> 06:01.661
[Metal squeaking]

06:03.032 --> 06:05.333
[Latch clicks]

06:05.334 --> 06:07.335
[Door clangs]

06:07.336 --> 06:10.304
Bam! The door came flying open...

06:10.305 --> 06:12.945
But it stopped.

06:17.054 --> 06:20.114
This was not natural.

06:22.124 --> 06:25.417
So I'm sitting there in my bed thinking
something's about to come around the door.

06:25.418 --> 06:30.218
Something's about to
come around that corner.

06:32.589 --> 06:35.289
And nothing did.

06:37.794 --> 06:40.554
[Unsettling music]

06:43.366 --> 06:46.846
So I got up out of bed...

06:49.205 --> 06:51.006
And I was terrified.

06:51.007 --> 06:54.427
I was absolutely terrified.

06:54.677 --> 06:59.777
I knew something was gonna
be around that corner.

