07:28.792 --> 07:32.032
There was nothing there.

07:34.817 --> 07:37.397
[Soft creaking]

07:38.488 --> 07:41.323
And then I had this sinking feeling...

07:41.324 --> 07:42.874
It's behind me now.

07:42.875 --> 07:46.415
[Suspenseful musical flourish]

07:56.972 --> 08:00.872
What was going on in this house?

08:01.643 --> 08:05.183
Do I really tell my family?

08:06.382 --> 08:09.951
They're gonna think I'm crazy.

08:09.952 --> 08:15.532
So at that point, I just
decided to keep it to myself.

08:15.991 --> 08:18.571
[Ominous music]

08:22.997 --> 08:25.517
[Baby wailing]

08:25.666 --> 08:29.202
- When's Daddy coming home?
- He's coming. He's coming.

08:29.203 --> 08:32.272
[Baby wailing, child laughs]

08:32.273 --> 08:34.900
At the time, I had seven children...

08:34.902 --> 08:38.636
Five younger ones and the two older.

08:38.638 --> 08:42.448
I had my work cut out for me
with those five little children.

08:42.450 --> 08:44.970
[Baby wailing]

08:45.886 --> 08:48.406
[Child laughs]

08:48.522 --> 08:54.102
It was just a lot of chores,
a lot of dishes to wash.

08:56.965 --> 09:00.167
There was no dishwasher
in the house. That was me.

09:00.168 --> 09:02.268
[Laughs]

09:04.739 --> 09:07.274
I would go outside and
play with my brother.

09:07.275 --> 09:13.175
We really loved it because
there was a lot of space outside.

09:16.050 --> 09:18.510
[Eerie music]

09:19.587 --> 09:24.507
I saw the ball go in
a hole in the outhouse.

09:26.894 --> 09:32.794
It seemed the thing to do was to
go in the outhouse and get the ball.

09:34.367 --> 09:35.171
[Knocking]

09:35.172 --> 09:37.287
Ken, don't move that.

09:37.288 --> 09:43.188
He didn't know that she had
told me not to move that rock.

09:45.733 --> 09:50.283
And I said, honey, honey,
don't move that rock.

09:50.284 --> 09:51.417
[Knocking]

09:51.418 --> 09:53.619
Don't move that rock.

09:53.620 --> 09:55.480
Ken!

09:56.390 --> 09:58.091
Don't move the rock.

09:58.092 --> 10:00.093
Let it be. We'll get another ball.

10:00.094 --> 10:01.761
Don't move the rock!

10:01.762 --> 10:07.134
It struck me as being mighty odd
because it required a lot of struggle.

10:07.135 --> 10:08.135
[Wind roaring]

10:08.136 --> 10:11.676
This gust of wind came out.

10:13.774 --> 10:17.014
We couldn't believe it.

10:18.634 --> 10:20.674
[Music]

10:22.481 --> 10:23.679
Don't move the rock!

10:23.680 --> 10:24.568
[Eerie music]

10:24.569 --> 10:26.249
_.

10:26.483 --> 10:28.343
Ken!

10:28.651 --> 10:31.171
[Wind roaring]

10:35.639 --> 10:38.140
It just knocked me back.

10:38.141 --> 10:43.722
And this thing's going down the
hallway and out the front door.

10:43.723 --> 10:46.630
[Eerie voices whispering]

10:46.631 --> 10:49.144
It wasn't like a gust of wind.

10:49.145 --> 10:52.745
It was like a ball of wind.

10:54.395 --> 10:56.530
It was a beautiful day.

10:56.531 --> 11:00.011
The weather was very still.

11:02.002 --> 11:04.528
This was definitely...

11:04.529 --> 11:08.369
Something that was beyond normal.

11:09.644 --> 11:13.497
What Pandora did they just unleash,

11:13.498 --> 11:16.738
out of that outbuilding?

11:18.135 --> 11:20.895
[Mysterious music]

11:29.663 --> 11:32.999
Something was just not right that night.

11:33.000 --> 11:35.580
[Soft creaking]

11:43.043 --> 11:46.883
I went to check the front door.

11:51.035 --> 11:53.435
Oh, my God.

11:54.379 --> 11:58.279
I just couldn't believe my eyes.

12:01.604 --> 12:03.939
[Discordant musical flourish]

12:03.940 --> 12:09.840
There was a man hanging in the
tree right in front of the house.

12:12.682 --> 12:15.982
I must be seeing things.

12:16.119 --> 12:18.999
I open the door...

12:27.282 --> 12:30.042
And it was gone.

12:36.006 --> 12:38.708
What have I just seen?

12:38.709 --> 12:41.289
What was that?

12:45.282 --> 12:48.968
I was really beginning
to worry about the place.

12:48.969 --> 12:51.387
And I didn't want to
tell anybody about it.

12:51.388 --> 12:54.688
It just really upset me.

13:01.231 --> 13:03.466
[Baby wailing]

13:03.467 --> 13:05.853
Once I'd started the course of studies,

13:05.854 --> 13:11.054
sometimes I'd have 11 or 12 hours in
the day when I was tied up with school.

13:11.055 --> 13:14.235
[Indistinct conversation]

13:15.245 --> 13:20.749
It felt like the family, at that time,
became second priority to his life.

13:20.750 --> 13:22.751
Honey, I... I'm sorry. I got to go.

13:22.752 --> 13:24.753
He really needs to be
changed right away...

13:24.754 --> 13:27.356
Wait, wait. Mom, Mom. Mom,
I got this. Let me help you.

13:27.357 --> 13:29.825
It's fine. I got it.

13:29.826 --> 13:34.149
My relationship with
Matt was rather trying.

13:34.150 --> 13:38.170
There was lots of tension in that.

13:38.501 --> 13:41.081
See you later.

13:49.146 --> 13:52.959
In the South, it's kind of
an unwritten rule that...

13:52.960 --> 13:55.897
When the father of the home is away.

13:55.898 --> 13:59.738
The eldest child fills the void.

14:05.262 --> 14:08.573
The weight of that comes down
on you, and you realize that,

14:08.574 --> 14:13.434
wow, I am now kind of
the man of the house.

14:14.637 --> 14:20.217
We were cleaning out the
house and cleaning out closets.

14:26.449 --> 14:28.909
[Eerie music]

14:35.391 --> 14:37.791
Oh, my God.

14:43.432 --> 14:45.934
It was really creepy.

14:45.935 --> 14:51.455
There were skeletons and
different little critter pieces.

14:55.545 --> 14:59.325
I didn't feel good about them.

14:59.615 --> 15:04.573
There seemed to be just
something that was going on...

15:04.574 --> 15:08.174
That just didn't feel right.

15:15.865 --> 15:18.625
[Eerie whispering]

15:19.362 --> 15:22.716
As I walked to the
house and I look up...

15:22.717 --> 15:25.674
I see a little girl
standing in the window.

15:25.675 --> 15:27.175
She's waving.

15:27.176 --> 15:29.878
I thought it was my
sister, so I waved back.

15:29.879 --> 15:34.019
I didn't really think a lot of it.

15:35.885 --> 15:37.719
But there's my sister.

15:37.720 --> 15:39.388
[Suspenseful musical flourish]

15:39.389 --> 15:44.429
It was like I'd been
just slapped in the face.

15:46.896 --> 15:50.856
Who was that that I'd just seen?

15:52.836 --> 15:58.441
As I'm going up the stairs, I'm
thinking, what am I gonna find?

15:58.442 --> 16:01.622
[Dark, unsettling music]

16:07.952 --> 16:11.072
I grab the doorknob...

16:20.213 --> 16:23.273
There's nobody there.

16:23.550 --> 16:29.450
I'm a little freaked out because
I know I saw somebody in there.

16:32.926 --> 16:35.506
[Ominous music]

16:43.337 --> 16:47.941
I was the only one who knew
this house contained secrets.

16:47.942 --> 16:49.609
I thought, all right.

16:49.610 --> 16:53.647
I've got to get to the bottom of this.

16:53.648 --> 16:56.719
I have this very close
friend named James,

16:56.720 --> 17:00.428
and we decided it was
time to get in that room.

17:00.429 --> 17:05.289
James and I were the
only ones in the house.

17:07.194 --> 17:10.797
The latch was not very well placed.

17:10.798 --> 17:15.202
They had left the screws
completely exposed.

17:15.203 --> 17:21.103
I took my multi-tool and removed the
screws that held the latch on the door.

17:24.779 --> 17:30.299
We don't know what's on
the other side of this door.

17:30.585 --> 17:36.485
The gruesome thoughts that go through
your mind is, a man died in here.

17:43.932 --> 17:47.601
- Did you get it?
- Yeah, I got it.

17:47.602 --> 17:48.832
[Exhales]

17:48.833 --> 17:51.533
Are you serious?

17:51.806 --> 17:52.815
[Sighs]

17:52.816 --> 17:56.143
We kind of looked at each
other like, okay, here we go.

17:56.144 --> 17:59.564
[Suspenseful music swelling]

18:03.617 --> 18:04.684
[Door creaks]

18:04.685 --> 18:07.253
[Ghostly breathing]

18:07.254 --> 18:12.174
This rush, whoosh! Came
over us of cold air...

18:12.883 --> 18:18.783
Which just didn't make any
sense because it was hot outside.

18:31.478 --> 18:36.998
I was hesitant to go into
the room after I opened it.

18:38.284 --> 18:41.824
It was like a time capsule.

18:43.969 --> 18:47.389
There was still a dresser.

18:48.874 --> 18:52.054
There was an iron bed.

18:53.511 --> 18:59.411
James and I looked at each other, and
we were like, is this where the guy died?

19:00.452 --> 19:04.712
Are these the sheets that he died in?

19:09.827 --> 19:11.927
[Sniffs]

19:12.630 --> 19:13.676
Do you smell that?

19:13.677 --> 19:17.757
I did notice a very peculiar smell.

19:19.737 --> 19:22.017
Cigarettes.

19:22.407 --> 19:24.009
This was fresh cigarette smoke,

19:24.010 --> 19:27.576
and this door had been
locked for God knows how long.

19:27.577 --> 19:31.357
And nobody in the house smoked.

19:33.244 --> 19:35.584
[Loud thud]

19:36.552 --> 19:39.479
And we heard this loud
crash, this loud bang.

19:39.480 --> 19:42.060
What was that?

19:42.160 --> 19:43.614
It was from upstairs.

19:43.615 --> 19:49.466
I was terrified, because I know
we're the only ones in the house.

19:49.467 --> 19:55.367
I look at James, James looks at me,
and we're like, we're going upstairs.

19:56.697 --> 19:58.737
[Music]

20:01.582 --> 20:03.262
_.

20:07.470 --> 20:09.150
_.

20:11.429 --> 20:15.209
I didn't know what we'd find.

20:21.572 --> 20:24.740
All of the doors were closed.

20:24.741 --> 20:28.444
We never keep these doors closed.

20:28.445 --> 20:34.345
We always leave these doors open. That's
how the heat radiates through the house.

20:34.618 --> 20:39.254
It was probably just a draft,
and it sucked one of them shut.

20:39.255 --> 20:41.089
I'm a very scientific guy.

20:41.090 --> 20:45.707
I approach things as there
is normally a, you know...

20:45.708 --> 20:49.521
Cause, a reason behind
something that happened.

20:49.522 --> 20:53.182
You spooked yourself. Come on.

20:59.242 --> 21:01.582
[Loud thud]

21:02.278 --> 21:05.818
Same sound, same loud crash.

21:07.952 --> 21:10.412
[Eerie music]

21:25.135 --> 21:28.555
[Suspenseful music swelling]

21:32.999 --> 21:36.299
The doors were all open.

21:36.880 --> 21:42.340
How is that possible when
I just saw them all closed?

21:48.591 --> 21:53.811
I just could not come up
with a valid explanation.

21:58.335 --> 22:01.935
I had a terrible realization.

22:02.172 --> 22:06.406
Perhaps that lock was not to
keep people out of the room.

22:06.407 --> 22:10.007
But to keep something inside.

22:23.593 --> 22:28.440
After I got the children
to bed, it was my habit...

22:28.441 --> 22:32.641
To go and just have some quiet time.

22:38.208 --> 22:43.968
But it was always kind of
edgy, and it wasn't relaxing...

22:48.852 --> 22:54.752
Especially as Ken's working hard
at college and I'm by myself.

23:03.600 --> 23:06.365
There was a tension...

23:06.366 --> 23:09.786
Like somebody was watching.

23:36.129 --> 23:41.278
I smelled smoke, but no one was
allowed to smoke inside the house.

23:41.279 --> 23:44.039
[Mysterious music]

23:48.545 --> 23:53.105
I could tell it was
coming from upstairs.

23:56.219 --> 23:59.519
[Thrilling music swelling]

24:02.459 --> 24:05.399
It was in my room.

24:06.429 --> 24:08.029
[Gasps]

24:08.030 --> 24:10.070
[Pants]

24:12.347 --> 24:17.438
There was a man standing, looking
out the window, smoking a cigarette.

24:17.439 --> 24:20.199
[Breathes heavily]

24:21.977 --> 24:26.177
I look back to flip the switch on...

24:29.417 --> 24:32.177
And he was gone.

24:35.490 --> 24:38.310
[Breathing heavily]

24:40.463 --> 24:42.503
[Gasps]

24:43.832 --> 24:45.692
Mom?

24:46.869 --> 24:50.693
I know I was running
off of very little sleep.

24:50.694 --> 24:53.742
But I know I saw someone.

24:53.743 --> 24:56.323
[Ominous music]

24:59.082 --> 25:01.765
I didn't want to tell you,
but when I was upstairs,

25:01.766 --> 25:05.487
I saw a man smoking in my bedroom.

25:05.488 --> 25:09.056
When she said that, my jaw
practically hit the floor.

25:09.057 --> 25:11.492
I'd smelled smoke in the padlocked room.

25:11.493 --> 25:14.495
- You smelled it too?
- Yeah.

25:14.496 --> 25:16.531
I told my Mom everything.

25:16.532 --> 25:18.599
I don't understand what's going on, Mom.

25:18.600 --> 25:22.078
The girl Matt had seen in the window...

25:22.079 --> 25:25.840
The hanging man, the smoking man...

25:25.841 --> 25:27.741
[Sighs]

25:27.742 --> 25:30.778
We knew there were ghosts in the house.

25:30.779 --> 25:33.419
[Glass shatters]

25:33.639 --> 25:36.219
What was that?

25:36.951 --> 25:41.211
This jar comes flying off the counter.

25:41.477 --> 25:43.091
What is going on?

25:43.092 --> 25:45.132
[Yelps]

25:45.227 --> 25:47.088
These things are flying across the room.

25:47.089 --> 25:48.229
[Shouts]

25:48.230 --> 25:51.933
Like someone was just throwing them.

25:51.934 --> 25:54.274
Bang. Boom.

25:54.368 --> 25:57.308
We're under attack.

25:58.781 --> 26:00.821
[Music]

26:02.619 --> 26:04.659
[Yelps]

26:06.712 --> 26:08.392
_.

26:12.472 --> 26:17.742
I felt like my children and
my family were under attack.

26:17.743 --> 26:20.803
[Eerie voice whispers]

26:21.078 --> 26:24.519
That night, I had just
terrifying nightmares.

26:24.520 --> 26:27.148
[Eerie voice whispers]

26:27.149 --> 26:33.049
This was something beyond scary dreams
and imaginary monsters under the bed.

26:36.823 --> 26:40.003
[Eerie voice whispering]

26:42.536 --> 26:48.431
In my dreams, there was an older
lady with kind of whitish-gray hair.

26:48.432 --> 26:51.612
[Eerie voice whispering]

26:55.036 --> 26:57.236
[Screaming]

26:57.237 --> 26:59.304
Mom! Mom!

26:59.305 --> 27:02.844
I was more terrified
than I can ever remember

27:02.845 --> 27:05.142
being at any other
point in time in my life.

27:05.143 --> 27:06.876
[Breathing heavily]

27:06.877 --> 27:10.297
Did you have a bad dream?

27:16.652 --> 27:21.887
It had gotten past the point of
just a little incident here or there.

27:21.888 --> 27:25.428
It had become really dark...

27:29.071 --> 27:30.859
And it wasn't just for me.

27:30.860 --> 27:34.662
It was for my little
children and for Matt too.

27:34.663 --> 27:36.883
[Sniffles]

27:41.335 --> 27:45.270
I realized that my Mom's not supermom.

27:45.271 --> 27:49.073
She's scared. She needs support.

27:49.074 --> 27:52.434
And I'm the oldest here.

28:00.449 --> 28:04.451
I was never much of
a believer in ghosts.

28:04.452 --> 28:07.268
I had been taught that
all along that if you...

28:07.269 --> 28:13.169
When you died, you went to one of
two places, either heaven or hell.

28:13.902 --> 28:17.682
What had happened in our house?

28:20.514 --> 28:24.602
I searched through years and
years of the local newspaper.

28:24.603 --> 28:27.570
Hoping to find an explanation.

28:27.571 --> 28:32.431
Just as I was losing
hope, I found something.

28:32.975 --> 28:36.409
A man hung himself in the front yard.

28:36.410 --> 28:39.650
[Eerie voices whispering]

28:41.615 --> 28:44.068
I started to dig some more.

28:44.069 --> 28:47.563
And then I found another
article, our house again.

28:47.564 --> 28:50.423
Another unnatural death.

28:50.424 --> 28:55.729
A young girl that had fallen down
the stairs and broken her neck.

28:55.730 --> 29:01.630
Could that have been the same
girl that I saw waving at me?

29:02.136 --> 29:06.706
This next article sent cold
chills through my entire body...

29:06.707 --> 29:09.347
A recent death.

29:09.875 --> 29:11.702
Another suicide.

29:11.703 --> 29:14.080
Could this have been the
Uncle of the previous tenants?

29:14.081 --> 29:16.049
[Eerie voice whispers]

29:16.050 --> 29:21.888
How could there be so many accidents
and suicides in this one home?

29:21.889 --> 29:25.489
This can't be a coincidence.

29:26.594 --> 29:30.730
Was there some sort
of curse on this house?

29:30.731 --> 29:33.491
[Unsettling music]

29:43.076 --> 29:45.596
All: Surprise!

29:45.645 --> 29:47.880
I was completely floored.

29:47.881 --> 29:49.329
Happy Birthday.

29:49.330 --> 29:51.617
They throw me a surprise birthday party.

29:51.618 --> 29:53.152
[Laughs]

29:53.153 --> 29:55.443
- Happy Birthday.
- Thanks. How's it going, man?

29:55.444 --> 29:57.691
- Come here.
- Long time, no see, right?

29:57.692 --> 29:59.955
With all the bad stuff that
was going on in the house,

29:59.956 --> 30:04.156
this was just what the family needed.

30:04.336 --> 30:10.236
It was really nice to have just some
time off from classes, off from studying.

30:13.396 --> 30:16.474
But when I found out
what was going on...

30:16.475 --> 30:18.741
What was happening in the house...

30:18.742 --> 30:21.906
How it was affecting my
children and my wife...

30:21.907 --> 30:25.084
I was worried about it.

30:25.085 --> 30:30.985
I was the man of the house, and I couldn't
be there all the time when they needed me.

30:31.559 --> 30:34.094
It made me feel guilty.

30:34.095 --> 30:37.095
Happy Birthday, Matt.

30:37.165 --> 30:41.335
But I saw a lot of development
in Matt during that time...

30:41.336 --> 30:44.756
Real heart to help others.

30:45.140 --> 30:47.141
A man's razor.

30:47.142 --> 30:49.722
[Ominous music]

30:59.883 --> 31:05.783
Later that night, I was standing
at the sink, getting ready to shave.

31:05.827 --> 31:08.887
[Eerie voice whispers]

31:11.599 --> 31:17.359
I looked down in the sink,
and I noticed something moving.

31:29.733 --> 31:34.113
This huge spider came out of the drain.

31:34.589 --> 31:39.152
Not a little spider... this is
huge, furry. Looked like a tarantula.

31:39.153 --> 31:42.273
I don't like spiders.

31:43.135 --> 31:46.975
And there's more in the toilet.

31:47.302 --> 31:50.345
And there was another one.

31:50.346 --> 31:55.056
They're just continuing
to come out of this drain.

31:55.057 --> 31:58.417
It's a flood of spiders.

31:58.975 --> 32:02.275
This is freaking me out.

32:07.053 --> 32:10.725
I was trying to scream
but couldn't make a sound.

32:10.726 --> 32:12.694
Where are they coming
from? This isn't normal.

32:12.695 --> 32:16.115
[Thrilling musical flourish]

32:21.568 --> 32:23.608
[Music]

32:25.466 --> 32:27.146
_.

32:27.329 --> 32:29.009
_.

32:29.523 --> 32:32.283
[Unsettling music]

32:34.313 --> 32:37.553
What am I going to do?

32:46.308 --> 32:50.568
I'm literally terrified at this point.

33:14.952 --> 33:17.772
I just couldn't help feeling
there was something in this house,

33:17.773 --> 33:19.603
and it was trying to kill me.

33:19.604 --> 33:22.364
[Eerie whispering]

33:25.051 --> 33:29.427
Now I was convinced that
this was not just ghosts.

33:29.428 --> 33:33.143
There's something else here
that is trying to get at us...

33:33.144 --> 33:39.044
Just like it got at the rest of
those families that had lived here.

33:39.653 --> 33:43.146
I'm thinking to myself, I
could walk away from everything,

33:43.147 --> 33:46.207
just to go and live with my father.

33:46.208 --> 33:52.108
But I knew that if I did that, no one would
be there to help take care of the family.

33:52.188 --> 33:57.108
I felt an enormous
responsibility come over me.

33:57.207 --> 34:00.447
It was time for action.

34:05.816 --> 34:10.498
Pastor Jimmy explained to me that
I needed to anoint this house.

34:10.500 --> 34:14.940
And he handed me a small bottle of oil.

34:15.943 --> 34:19.003
He entrusted me as...

34:19.237 --> 34:23.797
Someone who was mature
enough to do this.

34:23.860 --> 34:27.581
And that made me feel proud...

34:28.862 --> 34:31.983
But also very nervous.

34:32.243 --> 34:34.882
[Haunting music]

34:39.529 --> 34:45.429
Preacher Jimmy had told us we had to anoint
each other before we anointed the house.

34:56.560 --> 35:00.598
We have to do every point
of entry on this house...

35:00.599 --> 35:02.853
<i>He that dwelleth in the
secret place of the most</i>

35:02.854 --> 35:05.342
<i>high shall abide under
the shadow of the almighty.</i>

35:05.343 --> 35:06.711
<i>I will say of the Lord...</i>

35:06.712 --> 35:12.612
Every door, every window, every
surface, every point of entry.

35:13.618 --> 35:17.855
<i>He shall cover thee with his feathers,
and under his wings shalt thou trust.</i>

35:17.856 --> 35:20.570
<i>His truth shall be
thy shield and buckler.</i>

35:20.571 --> 35:23.902
<i>Thou shalt not be afraid
for the terror by night...</i>

35:23.903 --> 35:26.872
And then we moved to the roof...

35:26.873 --> 35:31.433
Because we were gonna
anoint the chimneys.

35:36.191 --> 35:41.849
<i>Only with thine eyes shalt thou behold
and see the reward of the wicked.</i>

35:41.850 --> 35:44.881
<i>Because thou hast made the Lord.</i>

35:44.882 --> 35:47.517
I got the first chimney.

35:47.518 --> 35:48.972
I anointed it.

35:48.973 --> 35:51.286
<i>There shall be no evil befall thee;</i>

35:51.287 --> 35:55.548
<i>Neither shall any plague come nigh thy
dwelling, for he shall give his Angels...</i>

35:55.549 --> 36:01.421
I crawled across the peak of
the roof to the other chimney.

36:01.422 --> 36:06.193
As I'm doing this, I
can feel a pressure...

36:06.194 --> 36:07.907
<i>He that dwelleth in the secret place...</i>

36:07.908 --> 36:12.468
Like everything is
closing in around me...

36:12.510 --> 36:15.581
Like I've got hands
crushing in around me.

36:15.582 --> 36:19.918
<i>He is my refuge and my fortress.
My God, in him will I trust.</i>

36:19.919 --> 36:24.023
<i>Surely he shall deliver...
[gasps] from the snare...</i>

36:24.024 --> 36:26.724
[Insects buzzing]

36:30.831 --> 36:36.469
And all of a sudden, I look down,
and there's a hornet on my arm.

36:36.470 --> 36:38.938
And the next thing I know,
there's hornets everywhere.

36:38.939 --> 36:41.639
[Hornets buzzing]

36:42.409 --> 36:46.300
<i>They shall bear thee up in their hands,
lest thou dash thy foot against...</i>

36:46.301 --> 36:50.517
I was terrified because I know
how allergic he is to stings.

36:50.518 --> 36:52.352
<i>Thou shalt tread upon...</i>

36:52.353 --> 36:53.820
This could kill him.

36:53.821 --> 36:58.225
<i>They shall bear thee up in their
hands, lest thou dash thy foot...</i>

36:58.226 --> 37:01.995
And I'm swiping. I'm trying
to keep them off of me.

37:01.996 --> 37:03.730
They were stinging him all over...

37:03.731 --> 37:05.212
<i>Thou shall tread...</i>

37:05.213 --> 37:09.203
His face, his neck, his arms, his chest.

37:09.204 --> 37:11.538
Feels like somebody punching you.

37:11.539 --> 37:13.365
I'm starting to slide down a little bit.

37:13.366 --> 37:16.786
<i>The lion and the dragon...</i>

37:33.461 --> 37:37.690
And I realized this
house could've killed me.

37:37.691 --> 37:41.568
I could have been its next victim.

37:41.569 --> 37:43.570
[Ominous music]

37:43.571 --> 37:47.108
It's physically attacking the children.

37:47.109 --> 37:48.949
I'm like...

37:48.950 --> 37:52.310
How much more can we do?

37:55.877 --> 37:58.294
I knew it was time to go.

37:58.295 --> 38:01.155
We had to... had to leave there.

38:01.156 --> 38:04.216
It just wasn't safe.

38:05.660 --> 38:09.533
We took the kids, we
packed up our things...

38:09.534 --> 38:12.954
And we were out of there.

38:12.967 --> 38:18.007
She vowed never to return
to that house again...

38:19.870 --> 38:25.770
But she wanted Ken and I to go and clean
it up and make sure it was presentable...

38:25.961 --> 38:29.758
When we gave it back to the owners.

38:29.759 --> 38:33.839
And that made me feel very nervous.

38:37.497 --> 38:40.130
I was in the room that had
the great big rug in it.

38:40.131 --> 38:42.591
[Eerie music]

38:51.706 --> 38:54.290
I pulled the corner of the rug back,

38:54.291 --> 39:00.191
and I see some strange markings
and some writing underneath the rug.

39:04.851 --> 39:07.971
[Eerie voices swelling]

39:09.889 --> 39:13.058
You could see markings and symbols.

39:13.059 --> 39:16.295
Wait. Can you help me over there?

39:16.296 --> 39:19.536
[Eerie voices whispering]

39:23.293 --> 39:25.333
[Music]

39:27.228 --> 39:28.416
_.

39:28.417 --> 39:32.377
Wait. Can you help me over there?

39:38.132 --> 39:42.036
We revealed this humongous Pentagram.

39:42.037 --> 39:44.503
[Eerie voice whispering]

39:44.504 --> 39:48.824
We knew this was a sign of witchcraft.

39:52.713 --> 39:55.716
We didn't even finish
cleaning that room.

39:55.717 --> 39:58.731
We just got out of there.

39:58.732 --> 40:04.632
A few minutes later, a shiny silver
Cadillac pulls up into the driveway.

40:06.294 --> 40:08.629
We had not yet met the landlord.

40:08.630 --> 40:10.932
I was expecting some old...

40:10.933 --> 40:16.833
You know, grumpy old man to
come showing up to get the keys.

40:20.042 --> 40:22.922
The door opens up.

40:28.008 --> 40:31.986
She was so beautiful,
it just seemed unnatural.

40:31.987 --> 40:35.167
[Eerie voice whispering]

40:35.791 --> 40:40.951
And she walked past me
and hardly acknowledges us.

40:44.619 --> 40:50.139
I look back, and two other
women got out of this car.

40:54.735 --> 40:59.314
The blonde lady comes back
through the screen door.

40:59.315 --> 41:02.315
She was just fuming.

41:02.334 --> 41:03.660
She demanded...

41:03.661 --> 41:07.689
What have you all done with this
house? There's nothing here anymore.

41:07.690 --> 41:10.992
She said, there are no spirits here.

41:10.993 --> 41:12.527
They've all left.

41:12.528 --> 41:15.264
There's no spirits here. They've
all left. They've all gone.

41:15.265 --> 41:20.936
She said to the other two, we'll have
to have a seance to bring them all back.

41:20.937 --> 41:22.437
What's going on here?

41:22.438 --> 41:25.798
[Unsettling music swelling]

41:28.113 --> 41:29.878
This is weird.

41:29.879 --> 41:32.021
It seemed like she had aged.

41:32.022 --> 41:35.817
I was mind-boggled. I
didn't know what to think.

41:35.818 --> 41:39.658
Y'all be careful in this house.

41:39.756 --> 41:43.776
Was I looking at the last tenants?

41:46.164 --> 41:47.729
Hey!

41:47.730 --> 41:50.999
Was I looking at the realtor?

41:51.000 --> 41:53.836
This was clarification for me.

41:53.837 --> 41:57.436
These women had been
practicing witchcraft.

41:57.437 --> 42:03.337
Perhaps these are the people
who have always owned the house.

42:06.349 --> 42:10.524
Had they created accidents
and unfortunate suicides...

42:10.525 --> 42:14.245
Filling the house with spirits?

42:15.423 --> 42:17.542
[Engine revving]

42:17.543 --> 42:21.743
I realized I'd never see them again.

42:26.169 --> 42:27.503
You're driving.

42:27.504 --> 42:31.104
[Reflective instrumental music]

42:32.090 --> 42:37.653
The experiences that you go through as
a teenager, traumatic or terrifying...

42:37.654 --> 42:42.600
Are what changes you and
molds you as an adult.

42:42.601 --> 42:48.501
Those four months in that long,
hot summer made me the person I am.

42:48.540 --> 42:52.874
It set me up for everything
that life could throw at me.

42:52.875 --> 42:54.555
_.

